{"tid":2516011,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"胡定旭：「忠誠廢物」說法有理由","createTime":"2021-05-04T11:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T14:34:19.000Z","uid":20933,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"42bc23bef8696d6c7b8fcdc722270303d24b9a0c","tid":2516011,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/13bb3d4f390196d8031ee526e23aaaa7/2021/05/1507a9835de38607b7c469605fc71d72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2F13bb3d4f390196d8031ee526e23aaaa7%2F2021%2F05%2F1507a9835de38607b7c469605fc71d72.jpg&h=7edc8816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全國政協常委胡定旭回應，早前全國港澳研究會理事田飛龍指，完善香港選舉制度後，中央需要的不是橡皮圖章或「忠誠廢物」說法。<br />\n<br />\n胡定旭認為有關說法有理由，指有些時候會有人好心做壞事及幫倒忙。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2390130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2390130&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK0BBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=5d213af8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2390130</a>"},{"pid":"dc477740f1c53acad4c1f7dc817b340d902b437f","tid":2516011,"uid":290118,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇嚟有好戲睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f5377f1a5304955ea74cf4a88166dd53f086b8","tid":2516011,"uid":99962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:11:11.000Z","msg":"鄉議局<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814f42809601e92f0515996bca2061e7ca9bfdca","tid":2516011,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:12:25.000Z","msg":"指有些時候會有人好心做壞事及幫倒忙  指雜近平？"},{"pid":"f47e6fda84